Crash rendering a RenderSettings scene with an empty arnold:filter on a RenderVar

An empty "arnold:filter" attribute on a RenderVar used to override the
box_filter default with an empty filter type, creating a null filter node that
was then dereferenced, crashing Arnold.

Repro scene reduced from a customer file (BUG_251128).

See #2677

author: cyril.pichard@autodesk.com

PARAMS: {'scene':'test.usda'}
